                                <div id="entry-1846" class="entry-asset asset hentry">
    <div class="asset-header">
    <h2 class="asset-name entry-title"><a href="http://www.chugensen.jp/member/2016/12/7-1.php" rel="bookmark"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">【会員限定】</span>&nbsp;7銘柄すべて満玉買い</a></h2>
